<div id="review_2377383982" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2377383982" />
    <a title="João Reis" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39677710-jo-o-reis"><img alt="João Reis" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1580338501p2/39677710.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2377383982?book_show_action=true">May 13, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="João Reis" class="user" itemprop="url" name="João Reis" href="/user/show/39677710-jo-o-reis">João Reis</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781846272769" href="/book/show/15956479-the-appointment">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2377383982" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15122249164206231164">4,5 stars, but taking into account my mental state in the last months, it surely deserves being rounded up to 5. Müller mixes present and past throughout the whole book and manages to get it superbly done, never sounding pretentious or false, and meanwhile tells some pretty good stories from Communist Romania.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


